@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Closed
Closed --> Archived : submit
Archived --> OnHold : update
Archived : entry / log shipment
OnHold --> Reviewed : submit
Reviewed --> Cancelled : process
Closed --> OnHold : revert
Cancelled --> [*]
@enduml